description: PRODUCT OVERVIEWMeet the phone that’s tiny, trendy and totally flex-worthy. With a full cover screen, you can reply to texts, preview photos and access even more widgets than before with your Galaxy Z Flip5 folded shut. And with Flex Mode, you can capture hands-free selfies and videos from any angle. A compact, durable design makes this pocket-sized phone perfect for life on the go. Plus, personalize your phone from the outside in with a customizable cover screen and four stylish colors to show off your style.
